你认识长爪？
You knew Longclaw?

367
00:24:56,496 --> 00:25:00,626
长爪跟她的族人 是我的部落针鼹一族的宿敌
Longclaw and her people were the sworn enemy of my tribe, the Echidna.

368
00:25:00,709 --> 00:25:05,714
我族光荣战死在他们手上 现在你将死在我手里
We fought and died at their hands,

369
00:25:02,903 --> 00:25:05,573
and now you will die at mine.

370
00:25:16,391 --> 00:25:18,560
快点上车，我是跟你一伙的
Come on. Get in! I'm on your side.

371
00:25:18,644 --> 00:25:20,562
不好意思，你哪位？
I'm sorry. Who are you?

372
00:25:21,813 --> 00:25:23,565
说实在的，我也不在乎
You know what? It doesn't matter.

373
00:25:26,109 --> 00:25:28,111
我们快离开，冲冲冲冲…
Get us out of here! Go, go, go!

374
00:25:32,324 --> 00:25:33,325
他有狂犬病
Ah! He's gone rabid!

375
00:25:35,577 --> 00:25:36,995
好恶，他在舔玻璃？
Gross! Is he licking it?

376
00:25:38,205 --> 00:25:39,498
掰啦
See ya!

377
00:25:39,581 --> 00:25:41,875
记得要去接种狂犬疫苗，蛋头
Make sure to get your shots, Eggman!

378
00:25:47,181 --> 00:25:49,250
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

379
00:25:49,383 --> 00:25:50,918
Whoa!

380
00:25:55,764 --> 00:25:59,434
太好了，能见到你本尊 是我最大的荣幸，索尼克
Wow. Okay. Let me just say

381
00:25:57,224 --> 00:25:59,159
it is an honor to finally meet you, Sonic.

382
00:25:59,518 --> 00:26:01,061
我可以叫你索尼克吗？
Is it okay if I call you Sonic? Everyone calls me Tails.

383
00:26:01,144 --> 00:26:03,939
大家都叫我塔尔斯，就是两条尾巴的意思
You're probably wondering why.

384
00:26:04,064 --> 00:26:06,358
所以说你有两条尾巴？
Let me guess. Because of the extra tail? That's right!

385
00:26:06,441 --> 00:26:08,360
没有错，其实很明显吧？
I should've known you'd get that. Cool.

386
00:26:08,443 --> 00:26:12,155
好喔，所以现在是怎么回事 蛋头回来了？
Also, what is going on? Robotnik's back?

387
00:26:12,239 --> 00:26:14,700
还有那个大红怪克里弗又是哪位
And who is Clifford the Big Red Rage Monster?

388
00:26:15,367 --> 00:26:17,327
他是纳克鲁斯，是最后一只针鼹
That's Knuckles, the last of the Echidnas

389
00:26:17,411 --> 00:26:19,830
是银河系中最危险的战士
and the most dangerous warrior in the galaxy.

390
00:26:19,913 --> 00:26:21,999
他沉迷于寻找王者翡翠
He's obsessed with finding the Master Emerald.

391
00:26:22,082 --> 00:26:24,418
你认真的吗？王者翡翠？
Are you serious? The Master Emerald?

392
00:26:24,501 --> 00:26:26,128
王者翡翠，那只不过是床边故事而已
That's just a bedtime story.

393
00:26:26,211 --> 00:26:27,629
但他相信那是真的
Well, he believes it's real.

394
00:26:27,713 --> 00:26:30,007
他觉得你就是找到它的关键
And he must think you're the key to finding it.

395
00:26:32,217 --> 00:26:34,052
红灯、红灯，方向盘给我
Red light! Give me the wheel!

396
00:26:34,136 --> 00:26:35,971
-嘿，你这是在… -脚挪开
Hey, what are you... Move your foot.

397
00:26:43,729 --> 00:26:45,022
应该甩掉他了
I think we lost him.

398
00:26:52,946 --> 00:26:55,532
我们没有甩掉他，我们真的没有甩掉他
We did not lose him.

399
00:26:53,981 --> 00:26:55,549
We definitely did not lose him!

400
00:27:00,787 --> 00:27:02,956
我有一个点子，你相信我吗？
I've got an idea. Do you trust me?

401
00:27:03,040 --> 00:27:05,250
当然不相信，我才刚认识你耶
Of course not! I literally just met you!

402
00:27:05,334 --> 00:27:07,419
-拜托让我…拜托 -你在做什么？
Just let me... Come on! What are you doing?

403
00:27:26,396 --> 00:27:27,648
我们在飞
We're flying.

404
00:27:28,357 --> 00:27:30,442
你的屁屁怎么变成直升机了？
Uh, did your butt just turn into a helicopter?

405
00:27:30,284 --> 00:27:32,953
A butt-copter!

406
00:27:31,818 --> 00:27:33,445
这是屁升机
Oh, only Sonic the Hedgehog could come up with something like that.

407
00:27:34,029 --> 00:27:37,366
只有音速小子索尼克，会说出这样的话

408
00:27:50,003 --> 00:27:54,475
Foxy move.

409
00:27:52,464 --> 00:27:54,633
好个狐狸尾巴

410
00:27:55,884 --> 00:27:57,928
想把事情做好
You want something done right...

411
00:27:59,221 --> 00:28:02,224
不如把事情都交给奴才代劳
You have to hire someone you can push around.

412
00:28:04,393 --> 00:28:05,394
惊叹号
All caps.

413
00:28:15,262 --> 00:28:21,435
<i>? I waited till I saw the sun ?</i>

414
00:28:21,568 --> 00:28:23,470
<i>? I don't know why I didn't come ?</i>

415
00:28:23,620 --> 00:28:24,913
博士
Doctor,

416
00:28:25,831 --> 00:28:26,957
你在哪里？
where are you?

417
00:28:33,755 --> 00:28:34,798
异类
Freak.

418
00:28:39,887 --> 00:28:41,805
（帮我准备拿铁）

419
00:28:43,056 --> 00:28:45,350
我…各位顾客抱歉
Oh, I, uh... I'm sorry, folks.

420
00:28:45,434 --> 00:28:47,811
我必须提早打烊，大家快出去
Uh, I have to close early. Everybody out!

421
00:28:47,895 --> 00:28:50,939
大家快出去，谢谢各位光临霸咖
Everybody out. Thank you for visiting the Mean Bean.

422
00:28:51,064 --> 00:28:53,108
好的，晚安…
All right, good night. Good night.

423
00:28:53,192 --> 00:28:55,194
（营业中）

424
00:28:55,277 --> 00:28:56,320
（休息中）

425
00:28:56,403 --> 00:28:57,863
（卫生检查A级…F级）

426
00:29:12,294 --> 00:29:13,337
他回来了
He's back.

427
00:29:15,047 --> 00:29:17,049
他回来了
He's back!

428
00:30:11,812 --> 00:30:14,064
这样子才象话嘛
That's more like it.

429
00:30:15,023 --> 00:30:17,860
我已经浴壳重生
I've been re-hatched!

430
00:30:29,413 --> 00:30:33,959
那么我这位豪大拳头好朋友
So, my massively metacarpaled friend,

431
00:30:34,042 --> 00:30:35,377
你提过…
you mentioned...

432
00:30:37,254 --> 00:30:39,256
终极的力量
Ultimate power.

433
00:30:39,339 --> 00:30:40,340
那是什么？
Back at the house?

434
00:30:40,424 --> 00:30:42,050
王者翡翠
The Master Emerald?

435
00:30:42,134 --> 00:30:43,510
这些跟你没关系
It does not concern you.

436
00:30:43,594 --> 00:30:46,597
我带你离开星球，你带我来找那只刺猬
I got you off that planet and you brought me to the hedgehog.

437
00:30:46,680 --> 00:30:48,765
我们已经不需要互相利用了
We have no more use for each other.

438
00:30:48,849 --> 00:30:51,185
我很不喜欢唱反调，但是…
Well, I hate to be a contrarian, but...

439
00:30:52,102 --> 00:30:53,228
还是有需要
I think we might.

440
00:30:54,730 --> 00:30:57,191
你以为这些机器打得过我？
You think these machines are a match for me?

441
00:30:57,274 --> 00:31:00,736
我会把它们像肋骨一样 拆成一根一根的…
I will shatter them like the bones from a fallen...

442
00:31:01,612 --> 00:31:02,738
它们是阶梯
Oh, they are stairs.

443
00:31:08,452 --> 00:31:12,623
你知道地球是我的地盘对吧
You see, Earth is my turf, G.

444
00:31:13,123 --> 00:31:15,876
如果你不会用牙线，肯定会走偏
If you don't know how to floss, you'll be lost without me.

445
00:31:15,959 --> 00:31:18,504
我听不懂你这句话是什么意思
I understand nothing of what you just said.

446
00:31:18,587 --> 00:31:22,966
我会帮你取回那颗翡翠 你再利用它，把…
I help you retrieve the Emerald, and you use it to...

447
00:31:24,259 --> 00:31:29,389
那只刺猬消灭
destroy the hedgehog!

448
00:31:29,973 --> 00:31:31,683
你是想要跟我结盟吧
You're suggesting an alliance.

449
00:31:31,767 --> 00:31:35,896
我们这的习惯是互相握手表示结盟
Around here we simply grip each other's hands tightly.

450
00:31:36,764 --> 00:31:39,533
Ow, ow, ow, ow, ow!

451
00:31:41,276 --> 00:31:44,905
你…这颗暴走的太空南瓜
You truculent space bumpkin!

452
00:31:44,988 --> 00:31:47,157
你捏坏我最喜欢的手
You've crushed my favorite hand!

453
00:31:47,824 --> 00:31:49,743
是吗？我的手没有怎样
Really? My hand is uninjured.

454
00:31:50,953 --> 00:31:53,205
不过我对你的承诺深信不疑
Ugh.

455
00:31:50,979 --> 00:31:53,047
But I'm now convinced of your commitment.

456
00:31:53,288 --> 00:31:55,207
赞赞
"Oh, goody,"

457
00:31:55,290 --> 00:31:58,794
他一边乔着关节一边说着话
he exclaimed, while he reset two of his knuckles.

458
00:31:58,853 --> 00:32:01,055
I'm...

459
00:32:01,296 --> 00:32:06,218
我很高兴我们愿意在同一队
delighted to be on the same team.

460
00:32:14,142 --> 00:32:15,435
公路旅行
Road trip!

461
00:32:16,019 --> 00:32:18,063
我可以让你把头伸出窗外
I'll let you stick your nose out the window.

462
00:32:20,274 --> 00:32:22,025
索尼克，我们在哪里？
Uh, Sonic, where are we?

463
00:32:22,109 --> 00:32:24,486
欢迎来到韦德的洞穴
Welcome to the Wade Cave.

464
00:32:24,570 --> 00:32:27,614
我原本想在有一天能对某位女人说的
Which is something I hope to someday say to a woman.

465
00:32:27,698 --> 00:32:29,366
是我妈以外的女人
A woman who's not my mom.

466
00:32:29,449 --> 00:32:31,410
韦德，专心一点
Wade, focus.

467
00:32:31,493 --> 00:32:35,205
要弄清楚为什么纳克鲁斯觉得 我是找到王者翡翠的关键
We need to figure out why Knuckles thinks

468
00:32:32,987 --> 00:32:35,056
I'm the key to finding the Master Emerald.

469
00:32:35,289 --> 00:32:37,207
还有他为什么会提到长爪？
And why did he mention Longclaw?

470
00:32:37,791 --> 00:32:40,043
当中一定有什么关联
There must be a connection.

471
00:32:40,627 --> 00:32:42,045
等一下，我知道了
Wait a minute. There is.

472
00:32:42,588 --> 00:32:46,508
你看，长爪给我的地图上 有一个翡翠的符号
Look. There's an emerald symbol on the map Longclaw gave me.

473
00:32:46,592 --> 00:32:48,468
我以前不知道那是什么
I never knew what it meant before.

474
00:32:49,178 --> 00:32:50,846
好像有什么反应
Something's happening.

475
00:32:50,705 --> 00:32:53,775
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

476
00:33:03,984 --> 00:33:05,360
长爪？
Longclaw?

477
00:33:05,444 --> 00:33:06,987
你好，索尼克，如果你看到这个
Hello, Sonic.

478
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:10,449
就表示我遭遇不测
If you're watching this, then something has happened to me.

479
00:33:10,532 --> 00:33:13,368
我祈祷你已经安全抵达地球
And I pray you've made it to Earth unharmed.

480
00:33:13,869 --> 00:33:18,165
这个世界之所以被选上 有着非常重要的理由
This world has been chosen for a very important reason.

481
00:33:18,248 --> 00:33:21,877
它就是王者翡翠所在的秘密地点
It's the secret location of the Master Emerald.

482
00:33:22,269 --> 00:33:23,738
Whoa.

483
00:33:24,004 --> 00:33:27,633
那颗翡翠的力量就是把想法转变为现实
The Emerald has the power to turn thoughts into reality.

484
00:33:28,133 --> 00:33:30,636
就跟《魔鬼克星》的棉花糖宝宝一样
<i>Like the Stay Puft Marshmallow Man from Ghostbusters.</i>

485
00:33:31,386 --> 00:33:35,474
如果在坏人手上 全宇宙的生命将会面临威胁
Shh!

486
00:33:31,879 --> 00:33:32,880
In the wrong hands,

487
00:33:33,014 --> 00:33:35,282
it could threaten all life in the universe.

488
00:33:35,557 --> 00:33:38,477
守护王者翡翠是我的神圣使命
Protecting the Emerald was my sacred duty.

489
00:33:38,560 --> 00:33:42,231
现在我必须把这个重大的责任交给你
And now I must pass that responsibility to you.

490
00:33:43,357 --> 00:33:46,026
现在是我的时刻
This is my moment.

491
00:33:46,109 --> 00:33:49,571
跟着地图走，找到翡翠以后把它守护好
Follow the map, find the Emerald, and keep it safe.

492
00:33:50,197 --> 00:33:51,740
亲爱的索尼克
My dear Sonic,

493
00:33:51,823 --> 00:33:54,785
你的心是我见过最善良的
you have a heart like no creature I've ever known.

494
00:33:55,410 --> 00:33:57,079
我真的很爱你
I love you so much.

495
00:33:58,747 --> 00:33:59,957
再见
Goodbye.

496
00:34:01,333 --> 00:34:03,126
不不…等等
No, no, wait.

497
00:34:10,259 --> 00:34:12,135
我不会让你失望，长爪
I won't let you down, Longclaw.

498
00:34:14,096 --> 00:34:17,224
刚才那位…是你爸？
So is that y-your dad?

499
00:34:17,306 --> 00:34:18,766
什么？
What?

500
00:34:18,851 --> 00:34:19,851
不是？
No?

501
00:34:20,601 --> 00:34:23,438
这张地图显示，第一条线索在西伯利亚
According to this map,

502
00:34:21,561 --> 00:34:23,064
the first clue is in Siberia.

503
00:34:23,522 --> 00:34:25,815
这是个能找到翡翠的罗盘
It's a compass that will lead to the Emerald.

504
00:34:25,899 --> 00:34:28,819
而且纳克鲁斯也来到地球，必须分秒必争
And with Knuckles already here, it's a race.

505
00:34:28,902 --> 00:34:29,902
纳克鲁斯？
Knuckles?

506
00:34:30,654 --> 00:34:32,447
我高中的时候也认识一个纳克鲁斯
I knew a kid in middle school named Knuckles.

507
00:34:32,531 --> 00:34:34,366
他可以吞下自己的拳头
Could fit his whole fist in his mouth.

508
00:34:34,449 --> 00:34:38,579
如果他们是同个纳克鲁斯，我们就完蛋了
If this is the same Knuckles...

509
00:34:36,343 --> 00:34:38,179
...we are screwed.

510
00:34:38,661 --> 00:34:41,081
你说的这两个纳克鲁斯都不是重点
This Knuckles, that Knuckles. It doesn't matter.

511
00:34:41,164 --> 00:34:42,833
我们要先抢先赢
We're gonna get there first.

512
00:34:45,835 --> 00:34:47,588
你说的“我们”代表…
What do you mean, "we"?

513
00:34:47,670 --> 00:34:48,964
就代表你跟我
You're coming with me.

514
00:34:49,047 --> 00:34:50,382
不不不…
Oh, no, no, no.

515
00:34:50,465 --> 00:34:53,677
我只是来这里警告你，我不是个外勤咖
I just came here to warn you. I'm not a field guy.

516
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:57,556
别担心，我会罩你的 我保证不会让你出事
Don't worry. I got your back.

517
00:34:55,428 --> 00:34:57,664
I won't let anything happen to you.

518
00:34:59,016 --> 00:35:02,769
这叫击个拳 地球上代表着坚不可摧的承诺
It's a power bump.

519
00:35:00,101 --> 00:35:02,737
On Earth, it means an unbreakable promise.

520
00:35:02,853 --> 00:35:05,564
好吧，我加入
Okay, I'm in.

521
00:35:08,209 --> 00:35:12,880
<i>? Me and you Maybe sunshine, maybe rain ?</i>

522
00:35:21,288 --> 00:35:23,665
博士，真的是你
Doctor. It's really you.

523
00:35:24,583 --> 00:35:26,126
你看起来很不同
You look different.

524
00:35:26,752 --> 00:35:29,421
因为老爸留了新的胡子
Papa's got a brand new 'stache.

525
00:35:30,264 --> 00:35:31,498
Ha!

526
00:35:32,549 --> 00:35:36,178
就知道，我就知道，我就知道你会回来
I knew it. I knew it!

527
00:35:34,202 --> 00:35:35,870
I knew you'd come back, sir.

528
00:35:36,261 --> 00:35:38,680
所以一直准备着奥地利山羊奶
I never stopped steaming your Austrian goat's milk.

529
00:35:44,603 --> 00:35:45,938
再加一点蘑菇
Could use some mushroom.

530
00:35:47,814 --> 00:35:48,982
你带回来，像是某一种…
You brought something.

531
00:35:49,733 --> 00:35:52,528
太空的豪猪
Some kind of, uh, space porcupine.

532
00:35:53,028 --> 00:35:56,031
什么豪猪？我可是一只针鼹
Porcupine? I am an Echidna!

533
00:35:56,114 --> 00:35:58,700
一出生就接受各种致命武术训练
Trained since birth in all forms of lethal combat,

534
00:35:58,784 --> 00:36:00,994
致力于恢复我族的荣耀
destined to restore honor to my tribe,

535
00:36:01,078 --> 00:36:04,873
如果敢挡我的路，就等着被我消灭
and willing to destroy anything that gets in my way.

536
00:36:05,499 --> 00:36:06,875
欢迎你的加入
Welcome to the team.

537
00:36:13,090 --> 00:36:15,008
这表示他相信你，石东
That means he trusts you, Stone.

538
00:36:15,634 --> 00:36:18,345
我们来改造这座垃圾堆
Now let's renovate this dump!

539
00:36:19,012 --> 00:36:21,348
来一杯奥地利山羊奶拿铁
Latte with steamed Austrian goat milk!

540
00:36:41,660 --> 00:36:42,911
好球，赞喔
Good one. Solid.

541
00:36:50,127 --> 00:36:51,461
抱歉，各位
- Sorry, fellas. - That's game!

542
00:36:52,588 --> 00:36:54,214
对，做得很好
Ha! That's how we do! That's how we do!

543
00:36:54,798 --> 00:36:57,176
-那他们数学强吗？ -团队合作让梦想成真
But are they good at math?

544
00:36:55,482 --> 00:36:57,550
Teamwork makes the dream work!

545
00:36:57,801 --> 00:36:59,136
不好意思，阿汤
Sorry about that, Big Tom.

546
00:36:59,761 --> 00:37:01,805
-你还好吗？ -没事，很好
Are you good? All good. Fine.

547
00:37:01,889 --> 00:37:04,933
嘿，谢谢你邀请我过来
Thanks for inviting me out to hang with you and your groomsmen.

548
00:37:05,017 --> 00:37:06,518
