You landed on our ice sculpture.

1090
01:10:00,409 --> 01:10:01,493
起来
Get up.

1091
01:10:07,474 --> 01:10:08,843
Just...

1092
01:10:09,209 --> 01:10:12,087
告诉我实话，拜托，就这一次
Just tell me the truth, for once.

1093
01:10:13,255 --> 01:10:17,426
关于你或我们之间有什么是真的？
Is there anything about you or about us that was real?

1094
01:10:18,218 --> 01:10:21,555
瑞秋，看着我，在认识你之前
Rachel, look at me.

1095
01:10:22,890 --> 01:10:26,518
我不认为我有机会得到真正的幸福
Before I met you,

1096
01:10:23,590 --> 01:10:26,660
I didn't think that I was even capable of real happiness.

1097
01:10:28,187 --> 01:10:30,439
遇见你之后一切都改变了
But that all changed when you walked into my life.

1098
01:10:31,565 --> 01:10:34,318
我还打破了卧底工作的第一条规则
And I ended up breaking the first rule of undercover work.

1099
01:10:35,027 --> 01:10:36,403
是什么？
Which is?

1100
01:10:37,154 --> 01:10:38,530
绝不坠入爱河
Never fall in love.

1101
01:10:51,710 --> 01:10:54,379
-麦蒂 -快点，我们快离开这里
Maddie! Maddie!

1102
01:10:54,463 --> 01:10:55,672
什么？你怎么通过守卫的？
We're busting out of here. How'd you get past the guards?

1103
01:10:55,756 --> 01:10:57,591
多亏我们有小狐狸的疯狂道具
Because that little fox is into some crazy stuff.

1104
01:10:57,674 --> 01:10:58,717
快点
Come on.

1105
01:11:00,302 --> 01:11:01,970
-我们走 -你太神了
Let's go. You're amazing.

1106
01:11:12,648 --> 01:11:15,317
愚蠢的猫头鹰还以为能藏住这个
The Owls were fools to think they could hide this.

1107
01:11:23,516 --> 01:11:25,086
Ah.

1108
01:11:53,772 --> 01:11:54,940
发生什么事？
What's happening?

1109
01:11:56,567 --> 01:11:58,235
等着瞧
Wait for it.

1110
01:12:09,788 --> 01:12:12,040
尤里卡
Yes. Eureka!

1111
01:12:13,250 --> 01:12:14,960
我找到了
I've found it!

1112
01:12:34,438 --> 01:12:35,564
索尼克
Sonic.

1113
01:12:37,524 --> 01:12:39,276
-那是什么？ -一个大麻烦
What is that? A big problem.

1114
01:12:40,319 --> 01:12:42,237
蛋头带着罗盘去找翡翠了
The compass led Robotnik to the Emerald.

1115
01:12:42,321 --> 01:12:44,323
那肯定是在几千英里外的地方
That's got to be hundreds of miles away.

1116
01:12:45,782 --> 01:12:49,203
好吧，靠过来，想一想计划
All right.

1117
01:12:47,101 --> 01:12:49,136
Huddle up. Let's figure out a plan.

1118
01:12:49,286 --> 01:12:51,330
-一起想 -已经没时间想了
Together.

1119
01:12:51,413 --> 01:12:53,373
我是唯一够快抵达那里的人
There's no time for that.

1120
01:12:51,839 --> 01:12:53,483
I'm the only one that can get there fast enough.

1121
01:12:53,457 --> 01:12:56,335
索尼克，这件事太重大了 你没办法独自承担
Sonic, this is way too big for you to do by yourself.

1122
01:12:56,919 --> 01:12:58,420
你们看到那边的小狐狸了吗？
You see that little fox over there?

1123
01:12:59,004 --> 01:13:02,007
他穿越了大半个宇宙来地球见他的英雄
He came all the way across the universe to meet his hero.

1124
01:13:02,090 --> 01:13:05,010
但是英雄做了什么？几乎害他失去了小命
And what did his hero do? I practically got him killed.

1125
01:13:05,886 --> 01:13:07,846
说真的，你是对的
You know what? You were right.

1126
01:13:08,388 --> 01:13:11,975
我的时刻到了，但没有把握住 我不是英雄
My moment came and I blew it.

1127
01:13:12,059 --> 01:13:13,227
-先等… -不
I'm no hero.

1128
01:13:13,310 --> 01:13:15,646
我不能再让别人因为我而受伤了
Wait. No.

1129
01:13:13,194 --> 01:13:14,594
I'm not letting anyone else get hurt

1130
01:13:15,729 --> 01:13:17,606
要趁来得及之前解决问题
because of me.

1131
01:13:15,963 --> 01:13:17,765
I'm gonna fix this while I still can.

1132
01:13:19,107 --> 01:13:20,734
索尼克
Sonic!

1133
01:13:20,817 --> 01:13:22,236
索尼克，等等
Sonic, wait!

1134
01:13:25,072 --> 01:13:26,949
不不…不可以，别乱动 别乱动，别乱动
Hold on. Wait. Don't move.

1135
01:13:27,032 --> 01:13:29,535
小家伙冷静点，你受伤了
Take it easy, little guy. You're hurt.

1136
01:13:29,618 --> 01:13:33,288
可是我们要帮他 你们不知道他要面对什么
But we have to help him. You don't know what he's up against.

1137
01:13:40,504 --> 01:13:41,880
现在相信了吗？
You believe us now?

1138
01:13:43,757 --> 01:13:45,392
Mm-hmm.

1139
01:13:49,012 --> 01:13:50,097
嘿，巴布
Hey, Bob!

1140
01:13:50,180 --> 01:13:51,932
嘿，玛丽亚你们好吗？
Hey, Maria, how you doing? Hey!

1141
01:13:52,066 --> 01:13:53,200
Ah.

1142
01:13:54,101 --> 01:13:55,394
（霸咖）
Working on my moves.

1143
01:13:55,477 --> 01:13:56,520
我只是练习一下
Just keepin' it green. No need to burn the fuel.

1144
01:13:56,603 --> 01:13:59,231
好的棒球经理不会在一开始就让球队

1145
01:13:59,314 --> 01:14:00,315
轻松出局，差不多…
Speaking of fuel...

1146
01:14:06,738 --> 01:14:08,115
休息中？
Closed?

1147
01:14:09,700 --> 01:14:10,909
不太对劲
That doesn't seem right.

1148
01:14:18,834 --> 01:14:21,962
（蛋头精品穿搭）

1149
01:14:23,714 --> 01:14:24,756
接近了
Close.

1150
01:14:29,303 --> 01:14:30,596
很好
Yes.

1151
01:14:30,679 --> 01:14:33,223
大改造，大改造，看看你
Makeover, makeover. Look at you.

1152
01:14:33,307 --> 01:14:34,641
警察，不准动
Freeze! Police!

1153
01:14:36,018 --> 01:14:38,103
欧买尬，你有机械手
Oh, my God, you got robot hands.

1154
01:14:38,187 --> 01:14:41,565
-不，这是手套 -举起来，快张开你的手指
No, they're gloves.

1155
01:14:39,280 --> 01:14:41,749
Get 'em up. Now spread your fingers!

1156
01:14:42,900 --> 01:14:45,527
现在甩一甩，甩甩你的手指
Now wiggle 'em! Wiggle your digits!

1157
01:14:46,987 --> 01:14:49,656
对，就像是你刚弹完一长串的曲子
Yes! Like you just finished a big musical number.

1158
01:14:51,491 --> 01:14:53,035
很好
Good.

1159
01:14:53,118 --> 01:14:54,536
你头上为什么有灯？
Why is there a light on your head?

1160
01:14:58,457 --> 01:15:00,501
因为我是周末专属的警长
'Cause I'm the sheriff for the weekend, pal.

1161
01:15:09,635 --> 01:15:10,594
水
Ugh. Water.

1162
01:15:10,677 --> 01:15:12,554
为什么一定要有水
Why did it have to be water?

1163
01:15:15,974 --> 01:15:18,310
好的，我办得到
Okay, you can do this.

1164
01:15:21,939 --> 01:15:23,524
加快速度
Gotta go fast.

1165
01:16:53,314 --> 01:16:54,815
Oh!

1166
01:17:06,126 --> 01:17:09,463
我不想就这样挂掉，这样太老套了
I don't want to die like this! It's derivative!

1167
01:17:11,006 --> 01:17:12,674
帮本大爷开路
Make room for Daddy!

1168
01:17:20,641 --> 01:17:21,808
两只、两只
Two and two. Great!

1169
01:17:21,892 --> 01:17:25,145
很好，我们还是双足动物，差不多啦
We're still bipedals, more or less.

1170
01:17:28,440 --> 01:17:29,983
要爆
Fire in the hole!

1171
01:17:32,194 --> 01:17:35,405
我算过，陷阱都是每七秒发生一…次
I've solved it. There is a booby trap every seven seco...

1172
01:17:42,079 --> 01:17:43,455
那个提早来了
That was a little early. Mmm.

1173
01:17:44,957 --> 01:17:48,544
幸好它没有切到我的胡子
Oh! So glad it didn't cut off my mustache.

1174
01:17:48,627 --> 01:17:51,046
嘿，前面这位小红炮
Hey, Little Red Wrecking Ball.

1175
01:17:51,880 --> 01:17:54,216
我知道你想快点得到翡翠
I know you're dying to get your Emerald on,

1176
01:17:54,299 --> 01:17:58,011
但是我们可能要多注意一下周遭的环境
but can we be a little bit more mindful of our surroundings?

1177
01:17:58,512 --> 01:17:59,555
借过
May I?

1178
01:18:06,186 --> 01:18:08,772
九公尺之后，左转
<i>In 30 feet, turn left.</i>

1179
01:18:08,856 --> 01:18:10,732
凡事都要事半功倍
Work smarter, not harder.

1180
01:18:32,171 --> 01:18:33,547
我要散了
My pelvis.

1181
01:18:37,926 --> 01:18:42,055
好的，秘密神殿，看你有多厉害
Okay, Secret Temple, let's see what you've got.

1182
01:18:48,362 --> 01:18:50,063
Whoa!

1183
01:18:50,197 --> 01:18:52,032
No, no, no! No!

1184
01:18:56,570 --> 01:18:57,571
不行
No.

1185
01:18:58,739 --> 01:18:59,740
好耶
Yes!

1186
01:19:05,704 --> 01:19:07,623
您已经抵达目的地
<i>You have arrived at your destination.</i>

1187
01:19:07,706 --> 01:19:10,709
这样让空间变宽敞
Wow. That really opened up the space.

1188
01:19:10,792 --> 01:19:13,754
我根本无法想象原本有墙的样子
I can't even picture it with an impenetrable wall now.

1189
01:19:13,837 --> 01:19:15,756
碎石一直都是很棒的装潢材质
And the rubble is always a nice touch.

1190
01:19:24,973 --> 01:19:28,685
终于见到了这个王者翡翠
At last. The Master Emerald.

1191
01:19:28,769 --> 01:19:30,020
终极的力量
Ultimate power.

1192
01:19:30,103 --> 01:19:32,940
很快就能够恢复秩序
Soon order will be restored.

1193
01:19:33,023 --> 01:19:36,360
全都多亏了你我之间的合作
All because of what we have done together.

1194
01:19:36,443 --> 01:19:38,737
多么动人的感言，纳克鲁斯
Such a lovely sentiment, Knuckles.

1195
01:19:39,238 --> 01:19:41,823
我感觉眼角好像泛泪了
I think I feel a single tear forming.

1196
01:19:44,785 --> 01:19:46,036
真可惜
Sadly...

1197
01:19:47,204 --> 01:19:51,750
你现在对我来说 只是一张过气乐团的演唱会通行证
You're as useful to me now

1198
01:19:48,388 --> 01:19:52,226
as a backstage pass to Limp Bizkit.

1199
01:19:52,359 --> 01:19:54,762
Whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa!

1200
01:20:06,431 --> 01:20:07,599
搞定
Nailed it.

1201
01:20:08,684 --> 01:20:12,229
这个家伙每次都来破坏我的坏事
This guy is always trying to spoil a bad thing!

1202
01:20:13,564 --> 01:20:16,066
你们两个也在这里？你们走远路J
Ah! You guys are here, too?

1203
01:20:16,149 --> 01:20:18,318
对你一切都是游戏吗？
Took the long way, huh?

1204
01:20:16,049 --> 01:20:18,118
Is everything a joke to you?

1205
01:20:18,402 --> 01:20:21,363
为什么你要一直阻碍我完成我的使命？
Why must you constantly interfere with my destiny?

1206
01:20:21,446 --> 01:20:25,117
因为我的使命就是保护我的朋友跟家人
Because my destiny is to protect my friends and family.

1207
01:20:25,200 --> 01:20:27,369
我刚才好像吐在我的嘴里了
I think I just threw up in my mouth.

1208
01:20:28,161 --> 01:20:33,375
如果你想得到翡翠，那就必须先打倒我
And if you want that emerald, you're gonna have to go through me.

1209
01:20:38,873 --> 01:20:40,340
Whoa!

1210
01:20:55,647 --> 01:20:58,692
无情的针鼹，今天一直往死里打
The Echidna's taking no prisoners today!

1211
01:20:58,817 --> 01:21:02,529
好心的索尼克这次难道会万刺俱灰吗？
Sonic has heart, but will he lose the quill to live?

1212
01:21:04,364 --> 01:21:08,035
我不想跟你战斗 可是你让我没有其他选择
I don't want to fight you, but you're not giving me much choice.

1213
01:21:14,750 --> 01:21:17,503
太容易了，准备办正事
Too easy. Let's do this.

1214
01:21:23,051 --> 01:21:24,484
Huh?

1215
01:21:44,655 --> 01:21:49,076
为什么你不乖乖站好光荣战死？
Why don't you stand still and die with honor?

1216
01:21:49,159 --> 01:21:50,410
让我考虑一下
Let me think about it.

1217
01:21:50,494 --> 01:21:54,164
好吧，考虑过了，然后我不要
Okay, I thought about it and I pass.

1218
01:22:03,632 --> 01:22:05,092
你好啊，小美人
Hi there, beautiful.

1219
01:22:06,385 --> 01:22:08,387
你是真实的，对吧？
You're the real deal, aren't you?

1220
01:22:09,096 --> 01:22:12,516
你这段时间都在哪里？

1221
01:22:16,353 --> 01:22:18,772
永别了，刺猬
Say goodbye, hedgehog.

1222
01:22:22,317 --> 01:22:25,195
纳克鲁斯，住手，你看蛋头想偷走翡翠
Knuckles, stop. Robotnik's stealing the Emerald!

1223
01:22:25,279 --> 01:22:27,739
你把我当成什么样的傻瓜？
What kind of fool do you take me for?

1224
01:22:27,823 --> 01:22:29,074
你自己看
Just look.

1225
01:22:31,618 --> 01:22:32,953
我的
Mine.

1226
01:22:34,204 --> 01:22:36,915
等等，我们的协议不是这样
Wait! That wasn't the deal.

1227
01:22:40,377 --> 01:22:43,005
你这只天真的可怜虫
Oh, you poor, naive creature.

1228
01:22:43,088 --> 01:22:44,506
不是你的错
It's not your fault.

1229
01:22:44,590 --> 01:22:48,218
高智商的人在一英里以外就会预料到了
A more advanced intellect would have seen this move coming a mile away.

1230
01:22:48,302 --> 01:22:50,137
或者是你们说的１.６公里
Or 1.6 kilometers.

1231
01:22:50,637 --> 01:22:53,390
但是我相信你，你是我的朋友
But I trusted you! You were my friend!

1232
01:23:00,522 --> 01:23:02,941
真抱歉，戳到我的笑穴了
I'm sorry. That just hit me funny.

1233
01:23:03,859 --> 01:23:08,906
我来帮你上我们的最后一课 你这个来自天边的呆瓜息肉
Let this be my final lesson to you,

1234
01:23:06,319 --> 01:23:08,923
you dim-witted celestial skin tag.

1235
01:23:09,865 --> 01:23:11,241
朋友
Friends...

1236
01:23:11,325 --> 01:23:15,329
必须要敞开心扉、互相包容才算朋友
are open, honest and vulnerable with each other.

1237
01:23:15,412 --> 01:23:17,956
这就表示Ｘ平方要乘以Ｙ平方的斜边
Which means X squared times the hypotenuse of Y squared,

1238
01:23:18,040 --> 01:23:20,876
然后再除以友情的绝对值，等于…
divided by the absolute value of friendship, equals...

1239
01:23:21,376 --> 01:23:22,419
渣渣
dookie!

1240
01:23:22,503 --> 01:23:23,754
糟了
Oh, no.

1241
01:23:31,887 --> 01:23:36,892
浑沌就是力量
Chaos is power!

1242
01:23:55,202 --> 01:23:56,954
我们快点逃出去
Let's get out of here!

1243
01:24:09,508 --> 01:24:10,676
纳克鲁斯
Knuckles!

1244
01:24:15,138 --> 01:24:18,016
怎么又是水，烦耶
Water again? Come on!

1245
01:24:37,812 --> 01:24:39,947
Mmm?

1246
01:24:40,081 --> 01:24:41,916
Mmm?

1247
01:24:42,049 --> 01:24:43,785
Mmm. Mmm.

1248
01:24:44,819 --> 01:24:45,987
Mmm?

1249
01:25:16,742 --> 01:25:20,746
-你救了我 -别跟我说话，我心情不好
You saved me.

1250
01:25:17,952 --> 01:25:20,721
Don't talk to me. I'm not in the mood.

1251
01:25:22,164 --> 01:25:26,168
你竟然敢攻击我 我现在心情非常难过
How dare you attack me in my hour of sorrow!

1252
01:25:27,044 --> 01:25:28,504
你为什么要救我
Why did you save me?

1253
01:25:30,547 --> 01:25:32,382
因为这次是你先救我的
Because you saved me first,

1254
01:25:32,466 --> 01:25:36,136
很明显，这样给了你一个 我不明白的战术优势
which clearly gave you a tactical advantage I do not understand.

1255
01:25:36,220 --> 01:25:39,848
这哪算什么战术，我不能就这样让你死掉
It wasn't a tactic. I couldn't just let you die.

1256
01:25:40,891 --> 01:25:45,604
为什么？从我们见面的第一刻开始 我就一直想解决你
Why?

1257
01:25:41,943 --> 01:25:45,213
I've been trying to destroy you since the moment we met.

1258
01:25:45,687 --> 01:25:49,608
因为只有照顾好自己 不能算是真正的英雄
Because being a hero isn't about taking care of yourself.

1259
01:25:49,691 --> 01:25:53,111
为了别人负起责任，才是真正的英雄
It's about taking responsibility for other people.

1260
01:25:55,405 --> 01:25:58,659
非常睿智，是地球古老的谚语吗？
Hmm. Wise words. An ancient Earth proverb?

1261
01:25:58,742 --> 01:26:01,161
并不是，这是华卓斯基家的格言
No, sir, that's a Wachowski family special.

1262
01:26:01,245 --> 01:26:03,247
某个划船大哥告诉我的
I got it from a guy in a rowboat.

1263
01:26:03,997 --> 01:26:05,499
他对我来说很重要
Someone who means a lot to me.

1264
01:26:07,417 --> 01:26:09,002
等等，那是什么声音？
Wait a second. What's that sound?

1265
01:26:11,171 --> 01:26:14,675
音速小子索尼克 才需要这么盛大的救援排场
Only Sonic the Hedgehog needs rescuing this much.

1266
01:26:15,843 --> 01:26:17,719
是聪明的小狐狸
That sly little fox!

1267
01:26:20,264 --> 01:26:22,599
来吧，那颗螺丝，我们还没输
Come on, Knucklehead. We're not beat yet.

1268
01:26:23,433 --> 01:26:25,936
在山上，你说过你失去了一切
On the mountain, you told me you'd lost everything.

1269
01:26:26,562 --> 01:26:28,063
我也一样
The way I did.

1270
01:26:28,146 --> 01:26:30,899
但你看起来很乐观又自在
But you seem so hopeful and free.

1271
01:26:31,900 --> 01:26:35,487
你是怎么继续前进？即便你失败了一次
How did you move forward despite failing again?

1272
01:26:36,238 --> 01:26:39,366
又一次…又一次…
And again. And again. And again. And again.

1273
01:26:39,449 --> 01:26:43,078
我没失败那么多次，因为我不是自己面对
Okay, I didn't fail that much. But I didn't do this all alone.

1274
01:26:43,161 --> 01:26:45,747
我找到了新的家庭、新的朋友
I found a new family. New friends.

1275
01:26:45,831 --> 01:26:47,249
你也可以的
And you can too.

1276
01:26:49,543 --> 01:26:51,962
你不需要继续独来独往
You don't have to be alone anymore.

1277
01:26:54,882 --> 01:26:56,884
Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!

1278
01:26:57,050 --> 01:26:59,219
你这样算哪门子的握手
Are you kidding me with that handshake?

1279
01:27:01,847 --> 01:27:03,265
我不要再当好好先生
I'm done playing games, pal.

1280
01:27:04,933 --> 01:27:06,685
告诉我，我想知道的事
You're gonna tell me what I want to know.

1281
01:27:09,104 --> 01:27:12,482
让我再问你最后一次
And I am asking you for the last time...

1282
01:27:14,818 --> 01:27:17,279
你的贝果要涂什么果酱？
what would you like on your bagel?

1283
01:27:17,362 --> 01:27:19,281
我什么也不会说的
I'm not telling you anything.

1284
01:27:19,364 --> 01:27:22,284
更何况，那是贝果的模型
And that is a display bagel.

1285
01:27:22,367 --> 01:27:25,579
我听不懂，因为我已经受够了
I don't get it with you! I mean, I've tried everything.

1286
01:27:25,662 --> 01:27:29,291
要扮白脸，又要扮黑脸 偶尔还要当送餐小弟
I was good cop. I was bad cop.

1287
01:27:27,048 --> 01:27:29,183
I was cop who offers you a bagel.

1288
01:27:29,374 --> 01:27:30,375
却什么也问不…
And nothing. It's like...

1289
01:27:30,459 --> 01:27:32,711
真的是模型
That is a display bagel. Wow.

1290
01:27:41,970 --> 01:27:43,722
博士，你在这里
Doctor, you're here.

1291
01:27:45,724 --> 01:27:50,395
对，我在这里
Yes, I'm here, and yet I'm...

1292
01:27:51,939 --> 01:27:53,607
所以我不在那里
not all there.

1293
01:27:53,690 --> 01:27:55,192
博士，一切还好吗？
Sir, are you feeling okay?

1294
01:27:55,275 --> 01:27:59,404
我好上加好
I'm more than okay.

1295
01:28:00,030 --> 01:28:03,158
我刚升级成
I'm upgraded.

1296
01:28:03,242 --> 01:28:06,286
阴险版三点零
Sinister 3.0.

1297
01:28:06,370 --> 01:28:10,374
游戏难度提升
My game is next level.

1298
01:28:15,462 --> 01:28:16,630
嗨
Hi.

1299
01:28:19,466 --> 01:28:25,639
我能够闻到你脑子里的那股电流
I can smell the electricity in your brain.

1300
01:28:27,474 --> 01:28:29,768
你闻起来像一盘点心
You smell like a snack plate.

1301
01:28:31,186 --> 01:28:34,314
对，很有道理，我今天吃很多
Yeah, no, that's fair. I had a couple today.

1302
01:28:34,857 --> 01:28:36,316
坐下
Sit down.

1303
01:28:40,988 --> 01:28:42,406
到椅子上
In the chair.

1304
01:28:45,617 --> 01:28:46,785
我弄不懂，因为坐椅子的人是他
I didn't know.

1305
01:28:47,870 --> 01:28:50,956
所以我…好吧
'Cause he was in the chair, so I didn't... Okay.

1306
01:28:51,039 --> 01:28:52,958
博士，出了点状况
Sir? We have a problem.

1307
01:28:58,538 --> 01:29:01,641
- All teams in position! - Set up a perimeter!

1308
01:29:01,776 --> 01:29:03,643
Move! Move! Move!

1309
01:29:18,609 --> 01:29:22,237
不正确（拉丁语），我所信赖的藤壶
<i>Incorrectus, my trusty barnacle.</i>

1310
01:29:23,572 --> 01:29:26,033
经过了这么多年之后
After all these years,

1311
01:29:26,700 --> 01:29:28,410
我终于找到了一个
what I finally got...

1312
01:29:29,578 --> 01:29:31,622
解决的好办法
is a solution.

1313
01:29:42,257 --> 01:29:44,134
-指挥官 -探员，报告状况
Commander. Status report.

1314
01:29:44,218 --> 01:29:47,596
蛋头和石东绑架了一个人质 好像是当地的警察
Robotnik is in there with Stone and a hostage. Possibly local PD.

1315
01:29:47,679 --> 01:29:51,058
我不是要说他笨，但他如果是当地警察
I'm not saying he's dumb, but if he is local PD,

1316
01:29:50,958 --> 01:29:53,327
this town's in a lot of trouble.

1317
01:29:53,519 --> 01:29:54,811
韦德
Wade.

1318
01:30:06,307 --> 01:30:08,008
Um...

1319
01:30:09,201 --> 01:30:10,202
好吧
Okay.

1320
01:30:11,161 --> 01:30:13,705
你这次穿的春季时装很潮
Rockin' that new spring collection, I see.

1321
01:30:13,789 --> 01:30:18,335
我记得你是酥皮大国王
Well, if it isn't the Pastry King.

1322
01:30:18,418 --> 01:30:19,545
是甜甜圈大王
The Donut Lord.

1323
01:30:20,045 --> 01:30:21,839
一个真正的天才应该要记住
A real genius would remember the name of the guy

1324
01:30:21,922 --> 01:30:23,841
把你一脚踹出地球的人叫什么名字
who helped kick your butt off this planet.

1325
01:30:23,924 --> 01:30:25,884
如果你敢惹绿丘镇我会再踹的
And I'll do it again if you mess with Green Hills.

1326
01:30:26,969 --> 01:30:30,764
还真是恭喜你拥有 这么一丝丝短暂又可悲的优越感
Congratulations on your oh-so-temporary sense of superiority.

1327
01:30:30,848 --> 01:30:33,183
你没戏唱了，蛋头，都被没收了
You're finished, Robotnik! We've taken everything.

1328
01:30:33,267 --> 01:30:35,978
实验室、无人机，还有资金
Your lab, your drones, your funding!

1329
01:30:36,061 --> 01:30:39,231
看你没有小小呆瓜机器人，你还能多自大
Let's see how big of a man you are without your silly little robots.

1330
01:30:40,983 --> 01:30:42,943
你们想看看我
Would you like to see how...

1331
01:30:44,361 --> 01:30:46,488
能自「大」到什么地步？
big a man I can be?

1332
01:30:57,374 --> 01:31:00,544
欢迎来到新常态
Welcome to the new norm.

1333
01:31:10,846 --> 01:31:12,222
天哪
My God!

1334
01:31:15,726 --> 01:31:19,438
博士，带我一起走
Doctor! Take me with you!

1335
01:31:43,879 --> 01:31:45,714
他正在摧毁一切
He's taking everything apart.

1336
01:31:46,715 --> 01:31:48,133
好像在组成什么
He's building something.

1337
01:31:56,141 --> 01:31:58,519
蛋头一定就在那附近
That can only be one thing.

1338
01:31:58,602 --> 01:32:00,979
翡翠的力量令人畏惧
The fearsome power of the Emerald.

1339
01:32:01,063 --> 01:32:05,067
如果它能把想法转变成力量 那我们的麻烦就大了
If that thing really turns thoughts into power,

1340
01:32:03,357 --> 01:32:04,959
we are in big trouble.

1341
01:32:05,150 --> 01:32:07,194
蛋头的脑袋有超多坏想法
Robotnik has a lot of bad thoughts.

1342
01:32:07,277 --> 01:32:10,239
索尼克，你确定带那一位上飞机
Hey, Sonic, are you sure it was a good idea

1343
01:32:10,322 --> 01:32:11,823
没有问题吗
bringing you-know-who aboard?

1344
01:32:11,907 --> 01:32:15,661
纳克鲁斯其实没那么坏 他只是有一点迷惘
Knuckles isn't really a bad guy. He's just a little mixed up.

1345
01:32:15,744 --> 01:32:17,454
我才没有迷惘
I am not mixed up!

1346
01:32:17,538 --> 01:32:22,417
我有坚定的意志 我也很复杂，一般人不会懂我的
I have steely focus. And I'm complex.

1347
01:32:20,741 --> 01:32:22,343
And that's a lot for some people.

1348
01:32:23,252 --> 01:32:25,879
希望你没把我开车撞你的事放在心上
Hope you're not still mad I hit you with that car.

1349
01:32:26,630 --> 01:32:28,382
我当时根本毫发无伤
Pfft! I was completely uninjured.

1350
01:32:28,465 --> 01:32:31,760
而且我会在你最意想不到的时候找你算账
And my revenge will come when you least expect it, fox.

1351
01:32:58,145 --> 01:32:59,380
Whoa.

1352
01:33:03,083 --> 01:33:05,669
博士，你真是太强了
Sir, you're magnificent!

1353
01:33:05,752 --> 01:33:07,796
谢谢，你这马屁精
Thank you, sycophant.

1354
01:33:07,880 --> 01:33:10,299
你会赞叹，这是当然的
Your admiration is inevitable.

1355
01:33:20,350 --> 01:33:21,810
我就知道
I knew it!

1356
01:33:21,894 --> 01:33:24,396
跟棉花糖宝宝一模一样
Just like the Stay Puft Marshmallow Man.

1357
01:33:25,480 --> 01:33:27,524
征服世界音乐列表
World Domination playlist.

1358
01:33:40,871 --> 01:33:42,039
撤退…
Fall back.

1359
01:33:43,457 --> 01:33:46,293
快点撤退
Fall back! Quick! Retreat!

1360
01:33:48,295 --> 01:33:50,380
要怎么样才能够击败那个机器人？
How are we supposed to beat this thing?

1361
01:33:50,464 --> 01:33:51,507
我们需要计划
We need a plan.

1362
01:33:51,590 --> 01:33:53,634
纳克鲁斯，用你的力量从…
Knuckles, use your strength to...

1363
01:33:54,218 --> 01:33:56,553
飞机上跳下去
Jump off the plane. Wow.

1364
01:33:56,637 --> 01:34:00,557
好吧，计划是这样子的 第一步，我们先闹一下
Okay, this is what we're gonna do. Step 1: Light taunting.

1365
01:34:00,641 --> 01:34:02,392
第二步…说真的我还没想到
Step 2: I have no idea.

1366
01:34:05,521 --> 01:34:06,688
索尼克
Sonic!

1367
01:34:09,858 --> 01:34:11,818
可动模型不错喔，蛋头
Nice action figure, Eggman.

1368
01:34:11,902 --> 01:34:14,821
它会做什么？除了丑还有其他的特色吗？
Does it do anything or just stand there looking ugly?

1369
01:34:18,492 --> 01:34:21,161
他就像水泡一样会一直回来
Like a blister, he keeps coming back!

1370
01:34:22,162 --> 01:34:25,123
他在杀戮清单上面，发射飞弹，果断一点
He's on the okay-to-kill list. Shoot the missiles. Make a decision.

1371
01:34:25,207 --> 01:34:28,001
请给我一点时间 我还在弄清楚该怎么操作
I need a moment, sir. I'm trying to figure out how to do this.

1372
01:34:28,085 --> 01:34:30,170
请问你翻过说明书了吗？
Did you even glance at a manual?

1373
01:34:30,254 --> 01:34:32,422
-不要 -让我来
No! I'll do it.

1374
01:34:32,506 --> 01:34:33,924
抱歉这么电
Pardon my lightning.

1375
01:34:34,007 --> 01:34:35,884
自己去接地一下
You might want to ground yourself.

1376
01:34:37,511 --> 01:34:38,946
Uh-oh.

1377
01:34:39,137 --> 01:34:41,682
我要把那个东西像罐头一样打开
I'm gonna pop that thing open like a can of chili...

1378
01:34:44,226 --> 01:34:45,686
坐稳
Whoa!

1379
01:34:44,084 --> 01:34:45,886
Hang on!

1380
01:34:47,621 --> 01:34:49,490
Whoa!

1381
01:34:51,892 --> 01:34:54,294
Whoa!

1382
01:34:56,964 --> 01:34:58,198
Whoo! Whoo-hoo!

1383
01:34:58,991 --> 01:35:01,243
-好耶 -好险
Oh, yeah! Whoo! Whoo-hoo-hoo! Close one.

1384
01:35:02,035 --> 01:35:03,120
索尼克
Sonic!

1385
01:35:06,874 --> 01:35:08,458
蛋头
Robotnik!

1386
01:35:10,085 --> 01:35:11,587
卑鄙小人
Deceiver!

1387
01:35:11,670 --> 01:35:13,422
蚊子去死吧
Die, mosquito.

1388
01:35:25,851 --> 01:35:26,852
很有感觉
Ooh! I felt that.

1389
01:35:39,506 --> 01:35:42,176
Oh! Whoa!

1390
01:35:46,038 --> 01:35:47,497
刚才怎么回事？
What just happened?

1391
01:35:47,581 --> 01:35:50,834
那招叫胡揍飞拳，说明书上写的
It's the Stache Masher. Right here in the manual.

1392
01:35:53,128 --> 01:35:55,464
退还给寄件人
Return to sender.

1393
01:36:03,055 --> 01:36:04,389
石东？
Stone?

1394
01:36:05,891 --> 01:36:10,062
太好了，接下来你就会控诉我 对你做出职场霸凌
Oh, great.

1395
01:36:07,067 --> 01:36:10,204
Next thing you know, there'll be a report about a hostile work environment.

1396
01:36:13,148 --> 01:36:16,318
我们的招都出完了，但是完全没用
Those were our best attacks, and they did nothing!

1397
01:36:16,443 --> 01:36:20,239
只要翡翠在蛋头手上 我们就没办法赢过他，他太强大了
We can't beat Robotnik as long as he's got that Emerald.

1398
01:36:18,780 --> 01:36:20,280
He's too powerful.

1399
01:36:20,322 --> 01:36:23,408
听着，我们各自分头进行 是没办法打赢蛋头的
Look, we aren't strong enough to beat Robotnik on our own.

1400
01:36:23,492 --> 01:36:24,743
但如果我们三个一起
But there's three of us.

1401
01:36:24,826 --> 01:36:27,996
你的力气、你的才智
Your strength, your smarts and my speed.

1402
01:36:28,080 --> 01:36:29,748
再加上我的速度，就能够获胜
Together. That's how we win.

1403
01:36:29,831 --> 01:36:34,294
所以我们几个一定要一起在战场上对抗他
So we make our stand here on the field of battle.

1404
01:36:34,378 --> 01:36:35,754
同心协力
As a team.

1405
01:36:35,838 --> 01:36:37,339
就是现在
This is it.

1406
01:36:38,715 --> 01:36:41,385
现在就是我们的时刻
This is our moment.

1407
01:36:43,428 --> 01:36:44,930
开打时间到
Time to fight.

1408
01:36:52,437 --> 01:36:55,858
虽然不是说这个的时候 但我还没有想到计划
Bad time to say this, but I don't actually have a plan.

1409
01:36:56,859 --> 01:36:58,694
塔尔斯，你有计划吗？
Tails, any ideas?

1410
01:36:58,777 --> 01:37:00,445
我们必须找到他的弱点
We have to find his weak spot.

1411
01:37:00,529 --> 01:37:02,155
我觉得是…鼠蹊部
I suggest the groin.

1412
01:37:02,239 --> 01:37:04,324
什么？不是，不是吧
What? No. No!

1413
01:37:04,408 --> 01:37:06,994
一般来说是的，鼠蹊部都很脆弱
Traditionally, yes, the groin is the weakest spot.

1414
01:37:07,077 --> 01:37:09,121
拜托，别再说鼠蹊部
Stop saying "groin."

1415
01:37:09,204 --> 01:37:10,998
刺猬
Hedgehog!

1416
01:37:11,081 --> 01:37:12,416
小心
Look out!

1417
01:37:15,210 --> 01:37:17,713
我知道他的弱点在哪了
I know what his weak spot is. It's me.

1418
01:37:17,796 --> 01:37:19,548
就是我，我是他的鼠蹊部
I'm the groin!

1419
01:37:22,176 --> 01:37:25,137
你们想想，他满脑子想要对付我
Think about it. Whoa!

1420
01:37:23,377 --> 01:37:24,979
I live rent-free in this dude's head.

1421
01:37:25,220 --> 01:37:27,055
如果我过去继续混淆他…
So if I go out there and rile him up...

1422
01:37:27,139 --> 01:37:29,558
他就只会注意到你，不会注意到我跟狐狸
He'll focus on only you, leaving himself open

1423
01:37:29,641 --> 01:37:31,894
从两侧发动攻击
to a flanking maneuver from me and the fox!

1424
01:37:31,977 --> 01:37:34,730
刺猬，你真是勇敢又高尚的战士
Hedgehog, you are a brave and noble warrior.

1425
01:37:34,813 --> 01:37:37,482
赶快带着光荣壮烈的牺牲吧
Go to your certain death with honor.

1426
01:37:37,566 --> 01:37:40,068
我要好好教教你什么叫说好话
We're gonna have to work on your pep talks, pal.

1427
01:37:40,194 --> 01:37:41,987
-没错 -我们走
Yeah. Let's go.

1428
01:37:45,699 --> 01:37:47,326
好的，大胡仔
All right, mustache.

1429
01:37:47,409 --> 01:37:50,245
想抓我，就要眼捷手快
You want me? Come and get me.

1430
01:37:50,329 --> 01:37:53,081
轮不到你叫我眼捷手快
You don't tell me about coming and getting.

1431
01:37:53,165 --> 01:37:55,542
我可是眼捷手快的第一把交椅
I am on the cutting edge of coming and getting!

1432
01:37:55,626 --> 01:37:57,544
眼明、手快
Coming, getting.

1433
01:37:57,628 --> 01:38:01,798
眼明、手快…
Coming, getting. Coming, getting. Coming, getting.

1434
01:38:04,384 --> 01:38:06,470
你真的好重
Oh, you're really heavy.

1435
01:38:06,553 --> 01:38:10,390
因为我全身百分之百都是肌肉 狐狸，飞快点
That's because I am one million percent muscle. Faster, fox!

1436
01:38:12,601 --> 01:38:15,771
-大家快跑，这边走，快点… -撤退，大家快快快…
Go! Move, guys! Move back! Let's go, that's it! Go, go, go!

1437
01:38:15,854 --> 01:38:16,897
-不要停，走 -快走…
Keep going! Go! Go!

1438
01:38:16,980 --> 01:38:18,857
-不不不… -停车，停下卡车！
No, no! Stop! Stop the truck!

1439
01:38:18,941 --> 01:38:20,234
汤姆，发生什么事了？
Tom, what happened here?

1440
01:38:21,276 --> 01:38:23,195
-你跟我想的一样吗？ -去救我们的孩子
You thinking what I'm thinking? Let's get our kid.

1441
01:38:23,278 --> 01:38:24,655
我们要你的车
We need your truck!

1442
01:38:30,869 --> 01:38:33,080
眼明、手快…
Coming, getting. Whew!

1443
01:38:34,015 --> 01:38:35,616
Yoo-hoo!

1444
01:38:36,166 --> 01:38:38,085
你接下来计划是什么？
So what's the plan here?

1445
01:38:38,669 --> 01:38:43,048
要盖一栋大机器人的房子？ 还是娶一个大机器人老婆？
Huh?

1446
01:38:38,552 --> 01:38:40,287
You gonna build a big robot house?

1447
01:38:40,420 --> 01:38:42,724
Get yourself a big robot wife?

1448
01:38:43,131 --> 01:38:47,469
我接下来要奴役人类 强迫他们服务我的机器
I'm going to enslave humanity and force them to service my machines.

1449
01:38:47,553 --> 01:38:50,389
绿丘镇先开始，再来是宇宙
First, Green Hills. Then the universe.

1450
01:38:50,472 --> 01:38:51,723
接着是多重宇宙
Then the multiverse.

1451
01:38:51,807 --> 01:38:54,601
然后谁知道，也许就够了
Then who knows? Maybe that'll be enough.

1452
01:38:55,185 --> 01:38:56,478
顺便告诉你
Full disclosure?

1453
01:38:57,354 --> 01:38:59,940
因为到时候你早就不存在
You won't be there.

1454
01:39:04,486 --> 01:39:06,613
眼睛雷射光？真的假的？
Eye lasers? Really?

1455
01:39:19,084 --> 01:39:21,044
鼻涕火枪
Snot rocket!

1456
01:39:22,629 --> 01:39:23,672
不不不…
No, no, no!

1457
01:39:30,237 --> 01:39:33,240
Giving up already?

1458
01:39:32,181 --> 01:39:33,682
你该不会放弃了？
Not so tough when you're fighting someone 700 times your size, are ya?

1459
01:39:33,765 --> 01:39:37,477
跟比你大七百倍的人打架 就嚣张不起来了，是吗？

1460
01:39:39,605 --> 01:39:42,065
你打不过我的
You can't beat me!

1461
01:39:42,149 --> 01:39:45,319
因为我无所不知、无所不能
I'm all-powerful! All-knowing!

1462
01:39:48,071 --> 01:39:50,282
无所不见
All-seeing.

1463
01:39:51,408 --> 01:39:53,744
看样子你的酷炫机器人故障
Looks like your fancy robot has a glitch.

1464
01:39:53,827 --> 01:39:57,080
我在这里，我也在这里
Is it me? What about me? I'm over here.

1465
01:39:55,863 --> 01:39:57,698
Up top! Down below! Behind you!

1466
01:39:58,081 --> 01:40:00,000
等等，我在那边，太慢
I'm over here. Sorry! Over here.

1467
01:40:00,626 --> 01:40:01,835
我在这边，还是没打到我…
Too slow! Try again.

1468
01:40:01,919 --> 01:40:03,962
-你智取不了我 -又没打中
You can't outsmart me. Missed me again.

1469
01:40:04,046 --> 01:40:05,839
我专门智取人
I'm the outsmarter-er!

1470
01:40:10,177 --> 01:40:13,138
我不是来智取你的，我只是来让你分心的
I didn't outsmart you. I'm just the distraction.

1471
01:40:13,222 --> 01:40:14,515
蛋头博士
Robotnik!

1472
01:40:15,140 --> 01:40:17,893
我也是立体投影
I am also a hologram.

1473
01:40:17,976 --> 01:40:19,895
无情无义
Disloyal.

1474
01:40:19,978 --> 01:40:22,814
“无”有吾的本色
"Dis" is how I roll.

1475
01:40:51,218 --> 01:40:52,761
我的翡翠在哪？
Where's my Emerald?

1476
01:40:53,512 --> 01:40:55,389
不不不…
No, no, no, no!

1477
01:40:55,472 --> 01:40:57,808
主计算机，开启辅助电源
Computer, auxiliary power.

1478
01:41:05,166 --> 01:41:06,768
Oh.

1479
01:41:07,150 --> 01:41:09,403
翡翠就在那里
The Emerald. It's right there.

1480
01:41:09,945 --> 01:41:11,864
动啊，你这堆废铁
Move, you hunk of junk!

1481
01:41:16,410 --> 01:41:19,788
我一定要拿到
I have to... reach it.

1482
01:41:43,020 --> 01:41:44,021
快点…
Come on.

1483
01:41:46,190 --> 01:41:48,358
他在那一边，开过去
There he is! Go! Go, go, go!

1484
01:41:57,284 --> 01:41:58,327
可恶
No!

1485
01:41:58,410 --> 01:41:59,703
我们救到你了
We got you, Sonic.

1486
01:42:00,913 --> 01:42:02,331
坐稳
Hold on!

1487
01:42:15,552 --> 01:42:17,804
-你们都还好吗？ -还好
- You guys okay? - Yeah.

1488
01:42:19,306 --> 01:42:20,349
很好
Okay.

1489
01:42:25,896 --> 01:42:27,940
我拿到翡翠了，还是能打败他
I got the Emerald. We could still defeat him.

1490
01:42:28,023 --> 01:42:31,193
快点…该怎么使用它？要怎么做？
Come on, come on. How does this thing work? What do I do?

1491
01:42:32,402 --> 01:42:33,570
什么？
What?

1492
01:42:34,238 --> 01:42:36,949
不不不…
No. No, no, no!

1493
01:42:40,827 --> 01:42:44,998
看看这个可爱又幸福的小家庭
Look at the happy little family.

1494
01:42:50,879 --> 01:42:53,382
你们要离我远一点，他的目标是我
You have to get away from me. I'm the one he wants.

1495
01:42:53,373 --> 01:42:54,641
Hey.

1496
01:42:54,967 --> 01:42:56,593
我们哪里也不会去
We're not going anywhere.

1497
01:42:57,177 --> 01:42:58,345
我们是一家人
We're family.

1498
01:43:01,932 --> 01:43:03,600
一家人就是无论如何
And families stick together...

1499
01:43:06,478 --> 01:43:07,688
都要在一起
no matter what.

1500
01:43:10,816 --> 01:43:11,942
我爱你们
I love you guys.

1501
01:43:12,860 --> 01:43:14,403
我们也爱你，索尼克
We love you too, Sonic.

1502
01:43:22,911 --> 01:43:24,371
不要
No!

1503
01:43:26,415 --> 01:43:28,584
干掉他啦
I got him!

1504
01:43:28,667 --> 01:43:32,254
我终于干掉他啦
I finally got him!

1505
01:43:37,718 --> 01:43:39,469
那个又是什么？
What was that?

1506
01:44:25,349 --> 01:44:27,559
全都结束了，蛋头
It's over, Eggman.

1507
01:44:27,335 --> 01:44:31,872
I like the new look. It works for you.

1508
01:44:28,936 --> 01:44:31,647
新造型很不错，非常适合你

1509
01:44:32,231 --> 01:44:35,234
我们就让过去的事过去，这样好不好？
What do you say we just let bygones be bygones?

1510
01:44:35,317 --> 01:44:39,071
我们两个都做过一些事 彼此都算是好人嘛
I did some things, you did some things.

1511
01:44:37,044 --> 01:44:39,113
There are good people on both sides.

1512
01:44:40,781 --> 01:44:43,867
两个天才一定能把这些纷争
Surely two intelligent beings

1513
01:44:45,619 --> 01:44:47,621
全部都解决
can work these things out!

1514
01:44:59,633 --> 01:45:02,094
-加油小子，上啊 -打倒他，索尼克
Come on, buddy.

1515
01:45:00,633 --> 01:45:02,036
Get him, Sonic! Come on.

1516
01:45:02,177 --> 01:45:03,512
很好，上啊
Yeah. Come on.

1517
01:45:20,070 --> 01:45:21,530
真的要这样吗？
It's like that?

1518
01:45:23,031 --> 01:45:25,325
好吧，我们不是麻吉
Okay, we're not friends.

1519
01:45:29,746 --> 01:45:32,040
先撤退，讨厌鬼
Later, hater!

1520
01:45:43,427 --> 01:45:44,887
-索尼克 -小子
Sonic! Buddy!

1521
01:45:45,470 --> 01:45:47,514
慢着，你们不能碰他
Wait! You cannot touch him!

1522
01:45:47,598 --> 01:45:50,267
刺猬现在拥有翡翠的力量
The hedgehog holds the power of the Emerald.

1523
01:45:50,976 --> 01:45:54,563
我很遗憾 他再也不是你们认识的索尼克了
I am sorry. He is no longer the Sonic you once knew.

1524
01:45:55,147 --> 01:45:56,148
什么？
What?

1525
01:46:14,574 --> 01:46:15,709
Mmm.

1526
01:46:16,084 --> 01:46:17,711
你们一定要试试看
Oh, you got to try this.

1527
01:46:23,467 --> 01:46:26,803
好吧，他就是你们认识的那个索尼克
Okay. He is exactly the Sonic you once knew.

1528
01:46:28,588 --> 01:46:30,124
Uh-huh. Uh-huh.

1529
01:46:38,524 --> 01:46:39,608
索尼克
Sonic! Whoa!

1530
01:46:41,944 --> 01:46:43,487
抱一个，小子
Bring it in, bud.

1531
01:46:44,947 --> 01:46:46,907
能变回蓝色真好
It's good to be back in blue.

1532
01:46:46,990 --> 01:46:50,327
金光闪闪是很帅啦 但蓝色还是比较适合我
The golden god thing was fun, but blue has always been more my color.

1533
01:46:50,410 --> 01:46:51,495
这样好看
Looks good on you.

1534
01:46:51,578 --> 01:46:57,000
索尼克，你原本可以成为 宇宙中最强的英雄，但是你放弃了
Sonic, you were the most powerful hero

1535
01:46:54,181 --> 01:46:56,984
in the universe, and you let it go.

1536
01:46:57,084 --> 01:46:58,168
为什么？
Why?

1537
01:46:59,920 --> 01:47:03,048
因为我还有很大的成长空间
Because I still have some growing up to do.

1538
01:47:05,300 --> 01:47:09,054
-而且当个孩子也不赖 -而且你不是普通的孩子
And I kind of like being a kid.

1539
01:47:07,595 --> 01:47:09,430
And you're not just any kid.

1540
01:47:09,638 --> 01:47:11,515
是我们的孩子
You're our kid.

1541
01:47:11,598 --> 01:47:13,016
说的对
That's right.

1542
01:47:13,100 --> 01:47:15,811
-抱一个 -抱抱
Bring it in! Yay. Hugs.

1543
01:47:15,894 --> 01:47:18,730
幸好你们刚才没来抱我，不然早就炸飞了
It's a good thing we didn't do this before. You would've blown up.

1544
01:47:26,363 --> 01:47:27,948
你修好了
Whoa! You fixed it.

1545
01:47:28,031 --> 01:47:31,368
我这辈子一直都在寻找这个东西
I've spent my whole life questing for this.

1546
01:47:31,451 --> 01:47:32,744
现在我找到了
Now I have it.

1547
01:47:32,828 --> 01:47:34,621
我们找到了
Now we have it.

1548
01:47:34,705 --> 01:47:37,291
该拿它怎么办，接下来呢？
What do we do with it? What next?

1549
01:47:37,374 --> 01:47:39,501
原本有两派英雄保护银河系
There were once two orders of heroes

1550
01:47:39,585 --> 01:47:43,714
他们要避免有人拿到翡翠作乱 让银河系受到伤害
who protected the galaxy from those who would use the Emerald for evil.

1551
01:47:43,797 --> 01:47:47,676
但现在他们都已经在天上的巨大战场了
But they have all passed on to the great battleground in the sky.

1552
01:47:47,759 --> 01:47:51,221
那我们自成新的一派，就我们三个
So we start a new order. The three of us.

1553
01:47:51,305 --> 01:47:53,015
这任务不容小觑
This is no light task.

1554
01:47:53,098 --> 01:47:57,728
一定要在此承诺 运用我们的力量守护整个宇宙的安全
We must make a vow to use our powers to keep the universe safe,

1555
01:47:58,562 --> 01:48:00,397
并且要照顾彼此
to watch out for each other.

1556
01:48:00,480 --> 01:48:02,191
我们的新部落
Our new tribe.

1557
01:48:02,274 --> 01:48:03,400
我知道了，击个拳
Oh, I know!

1558
01:48:03,483 --> 01:48:05,903
好主意
A power bump!

1559
01:48:04,818 --> 01:48:06,487
Good idea.

1560
01:48:06,945 --> 01:48:10,157
这是地球的习俗，代表坚不可摧的承诺
It's an Earth custom. An unbreakable promise.

1561
01:48:10,741 --> 01:48:12,034
没有问题
Very well.

1562
01:48:12,826 --> 01:48:15,245
我们就来击个拳
A power bump it is.

1563
01:48:16,413 --> 01:48:18,081
击个拳
Power bump!

1564
01:48:22,002 --> 01:48:26,131
今天晴空万里 真是一个在绿丘镇打棒球的好日子
It's truly a beautiful day

1565
01:48:23,737 --> 01:48:25,906
for baseball here in Green Hills.

1566
01:48:26,215 --> 01:48:27,925
阵容非常令人期待
An exciting lineup today

1567
01:48:28,008 --> 01:48:31,303
首次亮相的还有两位新球员
with the debut appearance of two new players!

1568
01:48:31,386 --> 01:48:35,557
投手丘上站着来自银河系的亮眼新秀
On the mound, rookie sensation from across the galaxy,

1569
01:48:35,641 --> 01:48:38,185
迈尔斯“塔尔斯”普洛尔
Miles "Tails" Prower,

1570
01:48:38,268 --> 01:48:42,981
他对上的是肌力满满的针鼹纳克鲁斯
facing off against the powerhouse, Knuckles the Echidna.

1571
01:48:44,441 --> 01:48:46,318
我不太明白
Um, I don't understand.

1572
01:48:46,401 --> 01:48:48,570
为什么要对敌人的球生气
Why am I angry at the enemy ball?

1573
01:48:48,654 --> 01:48:49,821
不需要生气
You're not angry.

1574
01:48:49,905 --> 01:48:53,158
只需要你尽全力打出去 然后跑过所有垒包
You just want to hit it as hard as you can

1575
01:48:51,732 --> 01:48:52,933
and then run around the bases.

1576
01:48:53,242 --> 01:48:57,871
可是如果我已经站在我要去的位置 为什么还要跑？
But if my quest ends where I am standing,

1577
01:48:56,403 --> 01:48:57,805
why run at all?

1578
01:48:58,539 --> 01:49:01,083
受不了这家伙，我干嘛找自己麻烦
Ugh. I can't with this guy. Why do I even try?

1579
01:49:01,166 --> 01:49:03,836
这只是一场游戏，全都是为了好玩
This is just a game. We're out here having fun.

1580
01:49:03,919 --> 01:49:05,420
只是好玩而已
Just having some fun.

1581
01:49:05,504 --> 01:49:06,922
好玩？
Fun. Huh.

1582
01:49:08,131 --> 01:49:10,509
很好，投个快球，塔尔斯
All right! Give him the heat, Tails!

1583
01:49:10,592 --> 01:49:12,511
准备好接我的快速球了吗？
Hope you're ready for my fastball.

1584
01:49:12,594 --> 01:49:15,097
你的快速球会无地自容
Your fastball will be dishonored.

1585
01:49:15,180 --> 01:49:17,391
你也一样，狐狸
And so will you, fox.

1586
01:49:17,474 --> 01:49:19,852
-大家放轻松点 -不需要想太多
Easy, guys!

1587
01:49:19,935 --> 01:49:23,355
把手肘好好稳住 眼睛看好球，送它去兜风
Don't think about it too much.

1588
01:49:19,994 --> 01:49:21,895
Just keep your elbow up, eye on the ball

1589
01:49:23,438 --> 01:49:24,857
兜风？去哪里？
and give it a ride.

1590
01:49:23,430 --> 01:49:24,999
A ride? To where?

1591
01:49:29,069 --> 01:49:30,404
击个拳
Power bump!

1592
01:49:35,701 --> 01:49:37,160
胜利属于我
Ha! Victory is mine!

1593
01:49:37,244 --> 01:49:39,788
不公平，这样不算吧
Hey, no fair! That shouldn't count.

1594
01:49:39,872 --> 01:49:42,124
第一垒，同样也是我的
First base is also mine!

1595
01:49:42,207 --> 01:49:46,795
-我们只有那颗球 -我占了第二垒
I think that was our only ball.

1596
01:49:43,884 --> 01:49:46,654
I have conquered the second of the bases!

1597
01:49:46,879 --> 01:49:48,422
好吧，谁想吃冰淇淋？
Who wants ice cream?

1598
01:49:48,505 --> 01:49:49,715
你的力气好大
Knocked the cover off that.

1599
01:49:49,798 --> 01:49:51,717
-冰淇淋 -冰淇淋，耶
Ice cream! Ice cream, yeah!

1600
01:49:52,968 --> 01:49:56,430
我终于得到“好玩”，什么是冰淇淋？
I am having the fun! What is ice cream?

1601
01:49:56,513 --> 01:49:59,850
是一种点心 如果你喜欢好玩，也会喜欢它
It's a dessert. If you like fun, you're gonna love it.

1602
01:49:59,933 --> 01:50:03,103
好吃，点心？里面有葡萄吗?
Oh, yum. Dessert. Does it have grapes in it?

1603
01:50:03,187 --> 01:50:04,771
没，一般来说没有
No, not usually.

1604
01:50:04,855 --> 01:50:06,523
我以他们为荣
I'm proud of our little guy.

1605
01:50:07,399 --> 01:50:10,444
我很喜欢他的新朋友 尤其是红色那一位
I really like his new friends, especially the red one.

1606
01:50:10,944 --> 01:50:13,572
-让我很开心 -还很会挥棒
He cracks me up. Heck of a swing too.

1607
01:50:13,655 --> 01:50:16,408
来吧狐狸，点心冒险在等着我们
Come on, fox.

1608
01:50:14,882 --> 01:50:16,517
Our dessert adventure awaits. Whoo!

1609
01:50:16,491 --> 01:50:17,826
-打得漂亮 -对啊
Good job, guys. Yeah.

1610
01:50:17,910 --> 01:50:21,205
你也是，宝贝 我们去吃冰淇淋 走，走吧
You too, baby.

1611
01:50:19,253 --> 01:50:22,056
Let's go get some ice cream. Come on, come on.

1612
01:50:22,372 --> 01:50:24,541
我真的很为你高兴
I'm happy for you, pal.

1613
01:50:24,625 --> 01:50:27,794
找到两个朋友，很适合一起成长
Got your wingmen.

1614
01:50:26,126 --> 01:50:27,461
Perfect friends to grow up with.

1615
01:50:27,878 --> 01:50:31,173
-上车，纳克鲁斯 -我的胜利战车
Come on, Knuckles. Ah! My victory chariot!

1616
01:50:33,217 --> 01:50:36,178
我得到的不只这些，老爹
I've got a lot more than that... Dad.

1617
01:50:41,642 --> 01:50:42,976
看谁先跑到那
Race you to the truck.

1618
01:50:44,645 --> 01:50:46,063
一二三，冲
One, two, three, go!

1619
01:50:46,647 --> 01:50:48,774
不能放水，我要你使出全力
No, don't go easy on me. I want your best.

1620
01:50:48,857 --> 01:50:51,818
索尼克，刚听说冰淇淋会加巧克力米
Sonic, I have just been told they have sprinkles.

1621
01:50:51,902 --> 01:50:55,572
冰淇淋加巧克力米？ 这就是你下一个要守护的
Ice cream and sprinkles? This is your new destiny.

1622
01:50:55,656 --> 01:51:00,577
我在棒子球上赢了你 很适合用冰淇淋当做庆祝大餐
What a perfect meal to celebrate my victory over you in base of ball.

1623
01:51:00,661 --> 01:51:03,288
-什么？ -说真的，你没打败我
What? I mean, you barely beat me.

1624
01:51:03,956 --> 01:51:06,458
你从没被打得那么惨过
Ha! You've never been beaten so hard.

1625
01:51:10,879 --> 01:51:12,047
不能忘了这个
Can't forget this.

1626
01:51:15,476 --> 01:51:17,746
<i>? Say I might And sail tonight ?</i>

1627
01:51:17,878 --> 01:51:21,281
<i>? I'm home ?</i>

1628
01:51:21,415 --> 01:51:23,684
<i>? Say right now, I'll get it ?</i>

1629
01:51:23,818 --> 01:51:28,857
<i>? Take my hand, come zone ?</i>

1630
01:51:28,989 --> 01:51:30,524
<i>? Come on, catch a ride ?</i>

1631
01:51:30,657 --> 01:51:34,194
<i>? And we take it to places That we only dreamed ?</i>

1632
01:51:34,328 --> 01:51:36,296
